POSSIBILIBITES NOW ARE up to you

UPDATE SYSTEMS

you can update all your systems via

sudo apt-get -y update

this will become:

pssh -i -h ~/.pssh_hosts_files -- sudo apt-get -y update


COPY FROM MAIN SERVER TO REMOTE HOSTS
you can copy a file from your main machine to all your remote servers!

  pssh -i -h ~/.pssh_hosts_files   $HOME/myfile.txt /$HOME/fileonservers.txt

  
